# Up-It-Up Cube Puzzle

<catsoop-section>Introduction</catsoop-section>

This cube-based challenge consists of eight cubes nestled inside a 3×3 box. The objective is to flip each cube from displaying a one-sided IIT Gandhinagar (flowered) logo to revealing a hexagonal logo of CCL, using minimal moves.

<catsoop-section>Materials Required</catsoop-section>

- MDF sheet

<center>
<img src="COURSE/algorithms/up_it_up/up_it_up_1.png" alt="Up-It-Up Materials" height="400"/>
